27 THE CORRECT CONTACT INFORMATION FOR A REPRESENTATIVE OF THE ENTITY
28 WHO HAS THE AUTHORITY TO COMMUNICATE WITH THE PUBLIC ABOUT THE ENTITY.
29 (2) THE CERTIFICATE SHALL BE:

