11 PROPOSED ALTERNATIVE HOUSING PRODUCTION TARGET BY SUBMITTING WRITTEN
12 JUSTIFICATION THAT INCLUDES:
13 (I) LOCAL DATA ON HOUSING NEED AND DEMAND;
14 (II) PLANNING AND ZONING CAPACITY;
15 (III) INFRASTRUCTURE AVAILABILITY OR CONSTRAINTS;
16 (IV) ENVIRONMENTAL OR TOPOGRAPHIC LIMITATIONS; AND
