15 SUBTITLE 4. QUALIFIED AFFORDABLE HOUSING PROJECTS.
16 12–401.
17 (A) IN THIS SUBTITLE THE FOLLOWING WORDS HAVE THE MEANINGS
18 INDICATED.
19 (B) “AFFORDABLE DWELLING UNIT” MEANS A DWELLING UNIT THAT IS
20 AFFORDABLE TO HOUSEHOLDS EARNING 60% OR LESS OF THE AREA MEDIAN
